We can replace every comma and semicolon occurrence with a token (DelimitToken) to create a PMF. A Tokens class can hold this tokenized text and in turn return it as the input for a lexical analysis process. We can generate our filtering algorithm to process this tokenized text and return the highest success probability for matching words.
